title: Ep 1952 - Bawris Parents in Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Jethalal gets a shock by knowing that Bawri’s parents have come again to Mumbai to meet Bagha. Jethalal calls Daya to inform about Bawri’s parents and gives strict instructions to Bagha and Bawri that he doesn’t want to meet

title: Ep 1953 - Bawris parents in Jethalals house
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal’s tension of avoiding Bawri parents in his house. He plans to leave Gokulham Society for few days and wants to return back after Bagha and Bawri’s engagement.

title: Ep 1954 - Jethalal Ka Balidaan
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Bawri’s parents spotting Jethalal having a cup of tea on his dining table. They get a shock on seeing him and thinks that Bagha servant is leading a luxurious life working in his house.

title: Ep 1955 - Baghas servant Jethalal
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Bawri’s parents considering Jethalal as Bagha’s servant. They are keeping a keen eye on Jethalal to ensure that he completes all necessary household work in timely manner.

title: Ep 1956 - Baagas secret is revealed to the society
shortDesc: Baavri’s parents have rented a flat in Gokul Dham society and this has created more troubles for Jetha Lal. When Bhide is about to reveal that Jetha lal is the owner of the house, Nattu Kaka becomes the saviour

title: Ep 1957 - Preparations for Baghas Engagement
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Bawri’s parent informing Champaklal about organizing Bagha and Bawri’s engagement. He further stresses that traditionally it is the groom’s side who bears all the expenses of engagement ceremony!

title: Ep 1958 - Baghas Truth
shortDesc: Everyone is Gokuldham Society is busy with the preparations of Bagha and Bawri’s engagement ceremony. The residents of the society are very happy for Bagha and Bawri but later in the episode, one of the relatives of Bawri

title: Ep 1959 - Bijli Devis googly for Jethalal
shortDesc: All the guests have started arriving to attend the engagement ceremony of Bagha and Bawri. Everyone is praying that the engagement rituals gets over very peacefully. It is then a woman named Bijli Devi

title: Ep 1960 - Bijli wants Daya to get married
shortDesc: Bijli, the sarpanch of Bawri devi’s village asks Daya to choose her groom before the engagement ceremony of Bagha and Bawri Devi. She cites about the practice which they follow in their community.

title: Ep 1961 - Bagha and Bawris Engagement
shortDesc: It’s the engagement ceremony of Bagha and Bawri and on a very important day of their life. Bawri’s parents come to know that both Bagha and Bawri has lied to them about Bagha’s profession.

title: Ep 1962 - Jethalals Confession to God
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal feeling relived after Bagha and Bawri’s engagement. He is feeling very relaxed and thinks that they have crossed all the barriers very calmly.

title: Ep 1963 - Bhide calls an urgent meeting
shortDesc: Bhide returns back from Pune and notices that there is a water leakage problem in the Gokuldham society. He decides to call an urgent meeting with the members of the society to discuss water leakage problem!

title: Ep 1964 - Bhide scolds Madhvi
shortDesc: Madhvi gets a good scolding from Bhide for misplacing her hard earned money. He points out that she was getting late to go for the Beauty Parlour and hence she was not careful at all.

title: Ep 1965 - Sonus Surprise for her friends
shortDesc: Sonu return’s back from her summer camp trip and surprises her friends by bringing beautiful gifts for them. She has brought Jackets for her friends, purse for Madhvi and Muffler for Bhide from Khufri.

title: Ep 1966 - Bhide questions Jethalal
shortDesc: Bhide gets a phone call from a parent, who asks Bhide to offer his tuitions to her child. Bhide gets excited thinking that he will get one more student for his tuition classes.
